title: Config Apply does not rediscover or reapply multi-profile settings
updated_at: "2026-07-15T05:57:19Z"
---
## Problem
Expanded “Refresh” only calls `refreshAll()`; there is no reload path when KCM config changes (`enabledProfilesJson`, `customProfilesJson`, `profileDisplayNamesJson`, `visibleWindowsJson`, `credentialsPath`, `provider`, etc.). Values are only read at `mergeDiscovered` / bootstrap time (except refresh intervals, which are read live). After Configure → Apply, the panel keeps the old profile set/names/visibility until Rediscover or plasmashell restart.

## Location
contents/ui/main.qml:549-554

## Suggested fix
`Connections` on `Plasmoid.configuration` (or specific keys) to re-run `discoverProfiles()` / rematerialize display names and `visibleWindowIds` without full plasmashell restart. At minimum, re-apply name/visibility patches without wiping fetch state.

